{"tid":1061983,"cid":19,"subCid":0,"title":"置富花園17歲少年身穿校服上吊　送院搶救不治","createTime":"2019-03-14T19:39:59.000Z","updateTime":"2019-03-19T07:39:45.000Z","uid":160807,"like":7,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":10,"replies":[{"pid":"64ae7a5f9e4a03d46a37e78765004c18159c37f7","tid":1061983,"uid":160807,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-03-14T19:39:59.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"http://static.stheadline.com/stheadline/inewsmedia/20190314/_2019031421213175625.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fstatic.stheadline.com%2Fstheadline%2Finewsmedia%2F20190314%2F_2019031421213175625.jpg&h=5eb09346&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n薄扶林置富道置富花園，晚上7時許，一名年約17歲的青年在富榮苑的單位內上吊，家人回家並發現後隨即報警。救護員接報到場，將事主解下，送到瑪麗醫院搶救後，但最終不治。警方正調查事件。據悉，事主被發現時身穿校服。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://hd.stheadline.com/news/realtime/hk/1456104/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhd.stheadline.com%2Fnews%2Frealtime%2Fhk%2F1456104%2F&d=%2FIrJ3RR%2Fwz8SFLZOEAJhpmzUwbN2nhMFbUYjFdDHJd4%3D&h=5cceb6d2\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhd.stheadline.com%2Fnews%2Frealtime%2Fhk%2F1456104%2F&h=e223e62c\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://hd.stheadline.com/news/realtime/hk/1456104/</a>"},{"pid":"4e8ce019ce9fc36a9e0466ae2e3d4fb8282d2f38","tid":1061983,"uid":144517,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-14T22:20:04.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"6c18feaaf439a6c9f5de454a9c28541ee24d0e54","tid":1061983,"uid":160807,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-15T00:34:22.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0e12386b0ffff583e54ee77af55fd83066fa881f","tid":1061983,"uid":79373,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-03-15T01:43:00.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />俾到住置富都已經係人生首抽SSR  好撚葡萄"},{"pid":"d871acc5583e98dc7b02e468ef4616a3